{"tid":1027881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堅強媽截肢 見愛女即笑","createTime":"2019-02-19T05:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T05:09:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"eb4e84b8c39c773f7aac4ae95116044ac602c37a","tid":1027881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190219/20615716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190219%2F20615716&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=82587a0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190219%2F20615716&h=8f246f53\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190219/20615716</a><br />\n<br />\n堅強媽截肢 見愛女即笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190219/large/a0902a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190219%2Flarge%2Fa0902a.gif&h=a9b3bedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事發當日被告駕寶馬鏟上行人路，壓向正候車的女事主。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】少婦杜穎楠遭被告寶馬撞上後倒地不起，左小腿以下位置當場斷開，斷肢在被告座駕車底尋回，她的右下肢亦遭嚴重壓扁，致骨頭及肌肉外露。惟當時她仍緊抱長女，忍痛問被告：「睇吓我BB有冇事？」事後她須注射嗎啡止痛，但仍心念愛女，手術後第一時間就是想見她們，當她跟兩名女兒視像通話時，開懷大笑，彷彿心肝寶貝就是最佳止痛藥。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：車鏟行人路 輾斷少婦腿 經紀稱發雞盲官：小朋友打機都識轉彎<br />\n<br />\n長女事後有情緒問題<br />\n<br />\n杜曾接受多次手術，她的胞姊早前透露，杜曾嘗試落床坐上復康椅，以爭取機會坐輪椅出病房看女兒。胞姊說杜得知要截肢後，「冇嗌過一句痛、流過一滴眼淚」。杜事後送院，證實右盆骨、右髖關節、大腿、小腿等身體多處骨折，左腳亦須截肢及裝上義肢。<br />\n<br />\n杜的長女則擦傷，事後有情緒及行為問題，患上創傷後壓力症候群。家人曾透露，意外後長女半夜疑受驚發噩夢，更哭着說「媽媽，腳腳痛痛」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭語霆<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n車鏟行人路輾斷少婦腿經紀稱發雞盲 官：小朋友打機都識轉彎<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隱瞞擁12幅地 男警涉騙學生資助"},{"pid":"b7d621a9274dd39c1785da655a572532d5e8c38b","tid":1027881,"uid":224058,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"母愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9a6bc60a68c561fbae1546ed75cd45ab184370","tid":1027881,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"金融狗定地產狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e57f0f1314b20d68d29bd173f0161281a4ff10","tid":1027881,"uid":79807,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"意外後長女半夜疑受驚發噩夢，更哭着說「媽媽，腳腳痛痛」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好慘好心酸"},{"pid":"24f1c390d22e3686fd3b97cea2dcee3ca7e335f8","tid":1027881,"uid":37413,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"好慘呢啲，法官如果輕判冇天理"},{"pid":"21a83581a4c98ab0386a56d62e696e6cd3660f96","tid":1027881,"uid":129340,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"真係睇一次火滾一次<br />\n屌你老母點先可以揸到咁<br />\n永久釘牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e28440506bbf1ec698a0edb3ccf806c338ff87","tid":1027881,"uid":169364,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"判條垃圾死刑未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e156054de223c352849066dff05a200c0caeb97","tid":1027881,"uid":153239,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4f9a6bc60a68c561fbae1546ed75cd45ab184370","tid":1027881,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"金融狗定地產狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:15:35.000Z","msg":"地產狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aeb55e18a52a7447e96e796ffb1efb05ef44b53","tid":1027881,"uid":19725,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08e284405